<TEXT>
Gerald Kaye, a former director of London &amp; Edinburgh Trust, has been
appointed development director of Helical Bar, which has development schemes
planned in Cardiff, Edinburgh, Leeds, Manchester, Coventry, Guildford,
Theale, Camberley, Hayes and Bristol.
Kaye, 35, is a chartered surveyor who started his career at Knight Frank &amp;
